```

Variables to configure:
- `LOCAL_DUMP_FOLDER`: Path to your dumps (e.g., `/mnt/disco8tb/dump`)
- `LOCAL_STAGING_FOLDER`: Staging path (e.g., `/mnt/disco8tb/cloud_staging`)
- `REMOTE_FOLDER`: rclone remote (e.g., `gdrive:LXC_Backups`)
